name: Laki-laki Luka
description:
Hello my friend this is my latest work!
From this work I used the Yashica FX-3 2000 Super camera with the expired camera roll film Lucky SHD 100. This work tells the story of a man whom I named Luka. Luka likes to go for walks in the afternoon, once he attends an art exhibition. 
Feet are the most important part of the human body. Without legs our life becomes unbalanced. I believe that our feet will always lead us to a good place. 
Because we are alive, our feet must always step forward even though our hearts carry wounds.
